<HL>
   Baker Forging New Soviet Economic Ties
   As Issues Such as Afghanistan Melt Away
   ----
   By Gerald F. Seib
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
09/16/91
</DATE>
